					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7964813#post-4022453</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7964813/scp-4030#post-4022453</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 13 Oct 2018 00:17:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zakinithos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4483447</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Very good SCP; an interesting premise executed well with good writing. +1. I did notice a small grammar mistake however; &quot;When worn, SCP-4030 will separate the <span style="text-decoration: underline;">wearers</span> body into its component organ systems as they translate through space.&quot; It should be &quot;wearer's&quot; with an apostrophe.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
