				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7964813/scp-4030#post-4022154</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 12 Oct 2018 15:32:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>BetterMyButter</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2818841</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>W-what? Hold up.</p> <p>Definitely came out of left field. I heard spooky looking blanket and expected some bland thing, but then it turns out to just divide you into pieces, which is pretty bizarre. But then it can make your skeleton sentient and <em>then</em> I realized this was a Halloween skip. Pretty solid, +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
